    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
