      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once the fish is cooked through, add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>smoked basa & leek cullen skink</strong></p>",
