    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoked basa & leek cullen skink</strong> in a bowl and sprinkle over your <strong>smoked sea salt</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> toasted ciabatta</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
